<activity xml:id="act-6-3-3"><title>Laws of Exponents</title>

<task><p>Simplify by using the laws of exponents. Write your answers using radicals.</p>
<p><ol cols="2">
  <li><p><m>x^{3/4}x^{5/4}</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>\left(x^{3/2}\right)^{5/2}</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>\dfrac{z^{1/3}}{z^{2/3}}</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>\dfrac{w^{1/5}w^{-3/5}}{w^{-4/5}}</m></p></li>
</ol></p></task>

<task><p>Simplify by using the laws of exponents. Write your answers using radicals.</p>
