<subsection><title>Wrap-Up</title>
<p>In this Lesson, we worked on the following skills and goals related to powers and roots:</p>
<p><ul>
<li><p>Evaluate powers with rational exponents</p></li>    
<li><p>Convert between radical and exponential notation</p></li>    
<li><p>Graph and analyze power functions with rational exponents</p></li>   
<li><p>Solve equations involving rational exponents</p></li>     
<li><p>Simplify expressions using the laws of exponents</p></li>
</ul></p></subsection>

<subsection><title>Questions for Writing or Discussion</title>
<p><ol>
